{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"30d4995d-bd45-4181-8f5e-eb3fb32b9854","content":"Here are the MSBuild evaluation performance issues I found:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Recursive wildcard glob (`**\\*.*`) — **High impact**\n**File:** `EvalHeavy.csproj`, line 9\n```xml\n<AdditionalFiles Include=\"**\\*.*\" Exclude=\"**\\bin\\**;**\\obj\\**\" />\n```\nThis forces MSBuild to walk the **entire directory tree** during evaluation to enumerate every file. As the repo grows, evaluation time grows linearly (or worse). If you only need specific file types, use a targeted glob like `**\\*.txt`.\n\n---\n\n### 2. File I/O via property function — **High impact**\n**File:** `EvalHeavy.csproj`, line 13\n```xml\n<BuildNotes>$([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('build-notes.txt'))</BuildNotes>\n```\n`ReadAllText` performs **disk I/O during evaluation**, which blocks the MSBuild engine. Property functions that touch the filesystem are especially costly because evaluation may run many times (IDE design-time builds, restore, etc.). Prefer reading files in a target at build time instead.\n\n---\n\n### 3. Deep import chain — **Medium impact**\n```\nEvalHeavy.csproj → level1.props → level2.props → level3.props\n```\nA 3-level chain of `<Import>` files increases evaluation time because each import is resolved and parsed sequentially. In this small project it's manageable, but this pattern doesn't scale. Flatten into fewer files where possible.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Issue | Location | Severity |\n|---|---|---|\n| `**\\*.*` recursive glob | csproj line 9 | 🔴 High |\n| `File::ReadAllText` during eval | csproj line 13 | 🔴 High |\n| 3-deep import chain | imports/ | 🟡 Medium |\n\nThe two high-impact fixes are: **narrow the wildcard glob** and **move the file read into a build target** instead of a property function.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f80ebd5b-cb41-4648-b2a2-a139d3215cfb","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me analyze the MSBuild evaluation performance issues in this project.","outputTokens":532},"id":"5f542cd9-bfc7-45a9-bab4-6b5718dd356b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:09:18.650Z","parentId":"eca6cbb0-8835-4c5a-95eb-f6ffbbf6eeed"}
